summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Moove fitness app. All major features working correctly including home page, video details, challenge functionality, search, and navigation.

ui_bugs.issue: Some bottom navigation buttons have visibility issues during automated testing

integration_issues.issue: Challenge cards on home page may not be properly linked to detail pages

passed_tests: Home page loads with featured workout and challenges sections
Video detail page displays with START WORKOUT, SAVE, and LIKE buttons
Video detail page button functionality (SAVE/SAVED, LIKE/LIKED state changes)
Challenge detail page loads and displays challenge information
JOIN CHALLENGE button functionality works correctly
Progress indicator appears after joining challenge (30% progress shown)
CONTINUE CHALLENGE button appears after joining
Challenge workouts tab displays 10 workout items with completion status
Search page loads with comprehensive filter options
Search functionality works with text input
Filter options work (Target Area, Category, Duration, Goals)
Video player interface displays with play button overlay
Challenge streak tracking shows (3 Days current streak)
